item.title: CVE-2018-12467|2024-08-05T08:38:06.304Z -- opensuse -- openbuildservice
item.description: Authorized users of the openbuildservice before 2.9.4 could delete packages by using a malicious request against projects having the OBS:InitializeDevelPackage attribute, a similar issue to CVE-2018-7689.
